## Object Detection – Initial Annotation Update

As part of the **Navya Project**, 41 images have been annotated using **Roboflow** for the initial object detection phase. The annotations follow a defined class taxonomy designed to support training for autonomous navigation.

### List of Classes
*(Final numeric indexing to be confirmed)*

- person  
- bicycle  
