- laptop  
- cell phone  
- sink  
- Static Obstacle  
- JCB  
- Trucks  
- obstacles-environment  

### Objective
To train a **YOLOv8** model for detecting and classifying navigation-relevant objects in campus environments. This work contributes to the perception system of the Navya autonomous vehicle by enabling it to identify static and dynamic obstacles.

